COMMAND EQUIVALENTS
Perbandingan Debian-based dan RedHat-based Linux

INSTALL PACKAGE

Debian / Ubuntu / Kali Linux:
sudo apt install nmap

RedHat / CentOS:
sudo dnf install nmap
(atau: sudo yum install nmap)

START SSH SERVICE

Debian / Ubuntu / Kali Linux:
sudo systemctl start ssh

RedHat / CentOS:
sudo systemctl start sshd

CHECK SERVICE STATUS

Debian / Ubuntu / Kali Linux:
sudo systemctl status ssh

RedHat / CentOS:
sudo systemctl status sshd

ADD FIREWALL RULE (ALLOW SSH)

Debian / Ubuntu / Kali Linux (UFW):
sudo ufw allow 22/tcp

RedHat / CentOS (firewalld):
sudo firewall-cmd --add-service=ssh --permanent
sudo firewall-cmd --reload

VIEW SYSTEM INFORMATION

Debian / Ubuntu / Kali Linux:
uname -a

RedHat / CentOS:
uname -a

KESIMPULAN SINGKAT:

Perbedaan utama terletak pada package manager, firewall, dan nama service SSH.

Perintah informasi sistem bersifat universal di seluruh distribusi Linux.

Pemahaman command equivalent penting untuk administrasi lintas distro.
